headline: Workday Announces Date of Fiscal 2026 First Quarter Financial Results
summary: Workday, Inc. (NASDAQ: WDAY), the AI platform for managing people, money, and agents, plans to announce its fiscal 2026 first quarter financial results after market close on Thursday, May 22, 2025. The company will host a conference call at 1:30 p.m. Pacific Time / 4:30 p.m. Eastern Time to review its financial results and business outlook.
